总结：服务端第一次接受 1024 byte 的数据，然后接收剩余部分；随后的每次都不拆包，而是接受完整数据  

Clinet 发送一段很长的数据  

```Java
// ...
.handler(new ChannelInitializer<SocketChannel>() {
    protected void initChannel(SocketChannel ch) throws Exception {
        ChannelPipeline pipeline = ch.pipeline();
        pipeline.addLast(new StringEncoder());
        pipeline.addLast(new ExampleClientHandler2());
    }
```

```Java
public class ExampleClientHandler2 extends ChannelInboundHandlerAdapter {

    private final String msg = "abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz" ; // 这里 msg 总长为 7286，先省略掉  
            

    @Override
    public void channelActive(ChannelHandlerContext ctx) throws Exception {
        ctx.writeAndFlush(msg);
        ctx.writeAndFlush(msg);
        ctx.writeAndFlush(msg);
        ctx.writeAndFlush(msg);
        ctx.writeAndFlush(msg);
        ctx.close();
    }

    @Override
    public void exceptionCaught(ChannelHandlerContext ctx, Throwable cause) throws Exception {
        cause.printStackTrace();
        ctx.close();
    }
}

```

服务端接收数据并打印  

```Java
// ...
.childHandler(new ChannelInitializer<SocketChannel>() {
    protected void initChannel(SocketChannel ch) throws Exception {
        ChannelPipeline pipeline = ch.pipeline();
        pipeline.addLast(new StringDecoder());
        pipeline.addLast(new ExampleHandler2());
    }
});
```

```Java
public class ExampleHandler2 extends SimpleChannelInboundHandler<String> {
    private int count;
    protected void channelRead0(ChannelHandlerContext ctx, String msg) throws Exception {
        System.out.println(msg.length());
        System.out.println(++count + " : " + msg);
    }

    @Override
    public void exceptionCaught(ChannelHandlerContext ctx, Throwable cause) throws Exception {
        cause.printStackTrace();
        ctx.close();
    }
}
```
